# --- legacy artefacts not worth versioning ---
# The full VDSensor/ tree carries third-party JARs (the original Java client +
# its predecessor VDMeeting builds). They live on the BBB and on the dev host
# as the protocol-RE source of truth, but we don't redistribute them via this
# public repo. CLAUDE.md still references them by their local paths.
VDSensor/
# Stray "echo 0 > value" leftover from the legacy Java LedsHandler in the wrong cwd.
VDSensor/value
# Stale 2014 setuptools shims pointing at a long-gone Python install.
/easy_install
/easy_install-2.7
# Broken symlink into /opt/source/beaglebone-universal-io/ on the original BBB.
/config-pin

